This framework allows us to test Cinderblock without the need to publish the package.

## Usage

1. Clone the ```https://github.com/teamfurther/cinderblock``` package
2. Go to the local folder where you cloned the package
3. Create an npm symbolic link in this folder: ```npm link```
4. Start working on cool new features
5. Clone this repo
6. Go to the local folder where cloned this repo
7. Type ```npm link @teamfurther/cinderblock```
8. Start testing!